There are sources for Android project [piHotKeys][1]
piHotKeys - app to control your PC with Android’s touchscreen using hot keys. No more “Ctrl-C”, “Ctrl-Shift-Z” or tons of other shortcuts to remember — just touch the button on the screen!

Project use AndroidBillingLibrary[2] for in-app purchase feature

[1]: https://market.android.com/details?id=name.pilgr.android.picat
[2]: https://github.com/robotmedia/AndroidBillingLibrary